{"tid":235162,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[徵求意見]開一間餐廳","createTime":"2017-05-08T19:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T07:29:32.000Z","uid":22906,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8780f179f5d1392ae77d67e562e255b6ccca01f","tid":235162,"uid":22906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:10:12.000Z","msg":"餐廳名叫Random<br />\n小弟既idea係想幫個客諗食乜 等啲有選擇困難既巴絲們有得玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先等位既時候會派張紙比客人剔選項:<br />\n人數<br />\n食物類別(eg set din, 小食, 飲品)但係冇得揀食咩<br />\n預計埋單價錢<br />\n食物敏感(if any)<br />\n<br />\n之後就係入去坐低等食 店主同廚師就跟住你既選項去製作食物 啲客人係未上菜之前係唔知自己將會食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能到上菜既時候你自己食緊拉麵 對面就可能食緊冬蔭公 而你想知自己要食乜就要到上左菜先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後埋單既價錢就係原來剔左個價錢range入面既價格<br />\n<br />\n個概念係因為見到啲人入到餐廳成日諗唔到自己想食乜 倒不如就由我地幫你諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲可以比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cc8f8c5c8059e854aee91cdd376108967702d6","tid":235162,"uid":19989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:12:01.000Z","msg":"賣飲品會唔會低成本D"},{"pid":"4d93a2d596278a91113193d556fe2affde2b1434","tid":235162,"uid":114304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:12:24.000Z","msg":"要搵一班好有心嘅廚師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持"},{"pid":"5b350a8539c2c2e65145558eca41cdb09952b449","tid":235162,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:27:47.000Z","msg":"叫是但，實好好生意"},{"pid":"def334fa64554007d76437fdff63a8779d39247c","tid":235162,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:28:56.000Z","msg":"G持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8351437bb020c9590c21cae0660732033b39b627","tid":235162,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:33:54.000Z","msg":"啱曬我呢啲選擇困難症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 真係開我一定黎試"},{"pid":"4123271021a24efa6e7ffeed890ba107ad9bad92","tid":235162,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T20:22:43.000Z","msg":"好似幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果唔太遠我會去試下"},{"pid":"64868ccea402317d8884bf1a4d0d6fdb10150be9","tid":235162,"uid":36414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T20:48:27.000Z","msg":"出到黎唔想食, 有冇得換?"},{"pid":"4ee647deaaa2dbce694429b4484f1228bda1875f","tid":235162,"uid":114976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:03:37.000Z","msg":"搵鬼同你做咩<br />\n要18般武藝先做得掂"},{"pid":"7d5659cca136d161d5d2d7a952c0c18eeb7fec40","tid":235162,"uid":50865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:23:05.000Z","msg":"一定大把仆街整左出黎唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395ced3c60868088bf6bb114162a70b77717fa45","tid":235162,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:28:04.000Z","msg":"有得做 大前提係你要真心好食"},{"pid":"39a36dce1df78d4fee241b96812dea656d3912a5","tid":235162,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:28:27.000Z","msg":"開餐聽好辛苦wo. 同埋呢個idea 回報mama 地"},{"pid":"8f5d6bb1f9cbc5d21e446262724a2d2111631a44","tid":235162,"uid":28031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:29:41.000Z","msg":"樓主應該0餐飲業經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你間野行高檔精品路線 <br />\n如果唔係只會玩尻食客玩尻廚師玩尻樓面最後玩尻埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者就變左一間random出a-e餐嘅茶仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e5c5559ed88a51bee51a6d1348c8b96f7abb51","tid":235162,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:31:52.000Z","msg":"慨念算okay<br />\n<br />\n但係現實未必work,你expect嘅係個個人打你份工都有你個heart,但問心，d廚房佬真係唔會咁好心機，所以個計劃好易比個廚搞彎曬，何況要煮多國菜，個廚份糧一定唔平，除非你搵到何志同道合嘅人合作"},{"pid":"01d57524b322368c4ad89690a4e66968db7361b1","tid":235162,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慨念算okay<br />\n<br />\n但係現實未必work,你expect嘅係個個人打你份工都有你個heart,但問心，d廚房佬真係唔會咁好心機，所以個計劃好易比個廚搞彎曬，何況要煮多國菜，個廚份糧一定唔平，除非你搵到何志同道合嘅人合作</blockquote><br />\nOverall就係你太理想化"},{"pid":"af5789d7a2da580a779ecf2a0c3529609c396257","tid":235162,"uid":37414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:34:28.000Z","msg":"最緊要開左唔好上黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8ee973d36c16b970ca6ec38c10d054bb3e2dd9","tid":235162,"uid":72631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:33:48.000Z","msg":"最後個廚師懶，叫是但嘅全部出同一款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3535e20000587652ec58a91830c461a87e8d8daf","tid":235162,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:54:57.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過個客自己帶材料比你地整菜式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8373efd7b0021db4dc0b7a8068aa385d6cb0e8b4","tid":235162,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:59:39.000Z","msg":"一定有廢老寫$20之後屌你份量小"},{"pid":"63b1c07ba1132ae83503b73bb2ac89c9c4c11d47","tid":235162,"uid":19627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:09:01.000Z","msg":"行唔通 <br />\n如果成枱人都叫同一個價錢 個個人食既都唔同<br />\n成枱人都會去諗 到底自己食個樣野值唔值 又或者點解人地個碟好似好食啲"},{"pid":"a39b1e41a64ef16cf226323e2ee089522beccf3b","tid":235162,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:13:08.000Z","msg":"到出餐 你仆硬街"},{"pid":"399f8635505e6cc4a978c77ef861f316606b66c6","tid":235162,"uid":26419,"like":0,"d